  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This observational study will acquire initial clinical practice utilization and product
      safety data for the Envision速 surface.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      This is a single site, open label, observational study to acquire initial clinical practice
      utilization information, product safety, and wound healing data, as defined by changes in
      wound volume and/or surface area, for patients with pressure ulcers placed on this surface.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
